<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184481>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Habitus (1 – 4) and metaventrite (5 – 8) of Scaphidium. 1, 5 — S. wuyongxingi sp. nov.; 2, 3, 7 — S. sinense (Baishanzu (2), Tianmushan (3 )); 4, 8 — S. stigmatinotum; 6 — S. comes. Scale bars 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/184481/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184482>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 17. Front (9 – 12) and hind (13) leg and antenna (14 – 17) of Scaphidium. 9, 14 — S. wuyongxiangi sp. nov.; 10, 15 — S. comes; 11, 16 — S. sinense; 12, 13, 17 — S. stigmatinotum. Scale bars 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/184482/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184483>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18 – 23. Aedeagus (18 – 20; dorsal view) and details of internal sac (21 – 23) of Scaphidium. 18, 21 — S. wuyongxaingi sp. nov.; 19, 22 — S. sinense; 20, 23 — S. stigmatinotum. Scale bars 0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/184483/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

